title: Elvis
description: Elvis is a prime selection from Seedism Seedbank in Amsterdam, leveraging insights from the Cannabis College. This AK47 hybrid is known for its potent effects and swift flowering period of 8-9 weeks. The genetic stability of AK47, combined with a quick flowering cycle, makes it a cornerstone in cannabis breeding efforts.

Elvis combines the intense Sativa high of AK47 with the sweet, skunky notes of Skunk#1, resulting in a complex flavor akin to sweet and spicy mango chutney. This crossbreeding results in a plant that flowers quicker, exhibits a stout appearance, and promises high yields for knowledgeable growers.
variety: Sativa dominant plant with Indica growth patterns
flavours: Sweet and spicy mango chutney, sweet, skunky notes

title: Purple Haze
description: Inheriting the best features of its parents, Purple Haze became a vigorous and high-yielding resin producer. Its long, big flowers are beautiful and full of trichomes, darker than most Sativas, more dark green of the Afghan varieties than the lime green of their equatorial counterparts.

This is a strain that provides uplifting sensations alongside heavy-hitting body effects. G13 was bred for maximum potency and is renowned for its medical utility, and it's not recommended for beginners!
variety: Mostly Sativa (Afghan x Haze)
medicinal: Uplifting sensations alongside heavy-hitting body effects, medical utility

title: Francoâs Lemon Cheese
description: After the tragic loss of Franco Loja beginning of 2017 the world has been waiting for a strain dedicated to Franco. The strain that would represent Franco the best could only be his very last cross of two of his favorite plants: The multiple cup winning Super Lemon Haze and the famous Exodus Cheese.

The plant grows tall with a strong main stem and long branches. The buds are round, medium sized and rock hard, covered in resin. The smell is very lemony with hints of Cheese in the background. When smoking the Cheese flavor is becoming more dominant on the exhale.
variety: Mostly Sativa (Super Lemon Haze x Exodus Cheese)
yield: Indoors: up to 750 gr/m2; Outdoors: up to 1000 gr/plant
flavours: Cheese, lemon
medicinal: Lack of appetite, pain, powerful, stimulating, talkative

title: Permanent Marker
description: Permanent Marker is a modern cannabis strain and is Leafly Strain of the Year 2023! Los Angeles indie brand Doja Exclusive released the Permanent Marker weed strain in 2022 on both coasts. Bred and grown by Seed Junky Genetics' JBeezy and selected by Doja Pak.

The strain fuses several well-established cultivars: (Biscotti x Sherb Bx) x Jealousy. It can smell like a permanent marker. Others note its floral, soapy, candy, and gassy funk that fully translate into the taste. The potent strain smells amazing, and can support creativity or relaxation day and night.
variety: Indica/Sativa hybrid ((Biscotti x Sherb Bx) x Jealousy)
flavours: Floral, soapy, candy, gassy funk, permanent marker
medicinal: Creativity or relaxation day and night

title: Fat Bastard
description: If you're looking for a strain that will really deliver come harvest time, make space for Blimburn Seeds' Fat Bastard. Fat Bastard pleases on many levels, including absolutely insane THC levels (30-38%). This plant is very adaptable in the grow room.

As a cross between Gold member and Monkey Spunk, the former brings Indica-dominant genetics and pungent aromas to the table, and the latter offers skunky, berry flavors and energizing effects. A few puffs will quickly elevate your spirits and give you an energy boost.
variety: Hybrid (Gold member x Monkey Spunk)
yield: Indoor: 400-600 g/m², Outdoor: up to 900g per plant
flavours: Skunky, berry flavors, citrus notes, pungent
medicinal: Elevate spirits, energy boost, soothing and relaxing

title: ORANGE VELVET UNDERGROUND RBX
description: Orange Velvet Underground is a beast in all phases, with baseball-sized nugs. Dark purple is her most common hue, but cold temps make her colors more vibrant and dynamic—almost blue.
Large, medium-dense kolas and side branching, baseball-sized nugs. Easily controllable and trained due to her strong lateral branching and vigorous, stacked apex growth.
variety: Hybrid ((Sour Tangie x Mandarin Sunset) x Orange Velvet)
flavours: Orange spices, earthy, skunky

title: La Bomba
description: La Bomba combines two incredibly vigorous, heavy-yielding and potent parents. This clone tend towards the terpene profile of Wedding Cake, which is a creamy Kush profile that may range from gassy to sweet like a confection.

Regardless of aroma, expect buds to be big and frosted with trichomes with roughly half of phenotypes fading purple. Both the parents are high-stretch, so the majority of the progeny from this cross will stretch 2x.
variety: 60% Indica, 40% Sativa (Wedding Cake x Jet Fuel Gelato)
flavours: Gassy, sweet

title: Critical aka Critical Mass
description: Our Critical strain is an Indica-dominant variety that stems from stoning parents Afghani and Skunk. She maintained a short size and rarely exceeds 100cm in height. It has short internode spacing, which will eventually fill up with buds.
Its small height also makes it suitable for those looking to grow in small spaces, for the more discreet growers, making it the high-yielding specimen it is.
variety: Sativa 40% Indica 60% (Afghani x Skunk)
flavours: Candy, earthy, fruity, pine, skunk

title: White Truffle x Garlic Sherb (unreleased)
description: White Truffles x Garlic Sherb is an unreleased and exceptionally rare strain bred by In-House Genetics, a brand known for its high-quality, exotic cultivars.
This powerhouse hybrid combines the rich, earthy depth of White Truffles with the pungent, savory profile of Garlic Sherbet, resulting in a strain that's both potent and flavorful.
variety: Hybrid (White Truffles x Garlic Sherb)
flavours: Rich, earthy depth with pungent, savory profile

title: Orangina Feminized
description: Orangina by The Grateful Seeds, a variety in Limited Edition ideal for lovers of strong sweet orange terpenes, with excellent results in extractions. Orangina is the encounter between Orange Jam (Agent Orange x Space Jam) and Orange Cookies (GSC x Orange Juice).

Orangina is a vigorous plant with beautiful colorations, growing in a shrubby shape with medium size and a large distance between nodes. It is ready to harvest in about 50-55 days, with great features to sieve the buds and obtain incredible extractions.
variety: Indica +60% (Orange Jam x Orange Cookies)
flavours: Fruity, citrus, milky & creamy, sweet, strong orange flavor with satuma and bergamot undertones

title: SUPER SILVER HAZE
description: The Super Silver Haze is one of the most famous Sativa strains in the world. Created by Arjan at the end of the 90's from a cross of Skunk x Northern Lights x Haze, it instantly won numerous 1st Place prizes at the High Times Cannabis Cup.

The result is a beautiful Sativa-dominant plant with the yield and flower appeal of some of the prettiest Indica's. The taste is a complex mix of the Haze ancestors, the Skunk and the Northern Lights. The high is instant and strong, great for any occasion, party or brainstorming session.
variety: 70% Sativa - 30% Indica (Skunk x Northern Lights x Haze)
height: stretch 2-3x during flowering, can become huge tree
yield: Indoor: up to 800 gr/m², Outdoor: up to 1500 gr/plant
flavours: Strong pine-tree and woody taste, sweetness of skunk, light metallic notes
medicinal: Psychoactive, instant and strong, long lasting effect, active

title: Kosher Kush Breath
description: Kosher Kush Breath is a hybrid strain that has been reported to help patients with menstrual symptoms, mood stabilization, and anti-inflammation. A great strain for helping you get through the stresses of the daily grind.
If you need a little afternoon pick me up, or you need something to help when it is that time of the month, Kosher Kush Breath has got you covered.
variety: Hybrid
medicinal: Menstrual symptoms, mood stabilization, anti-inflammation, stress relief

title: Blackberry Moonrocks
description: Blackberry Moonrocks follows in the footsteps of other legendary and unique strains of our Seedbank. It was developed from a selected extremely potent female Blue Moonrock and a male Blackberry Kush, which has a particularly pronounced terpene and cannabinoid profile.

This strain is not recommended for faint-hearteds and beginners, as its gigantic THC content of 32% and the extensive cannabinoid profile ensure long-lasting and very intense effects. The effect is mainly Indica dominant, very strong and is complemented by inspiring mood-enhancing Sativa effects.
variety: 80% Indica, 20% Sativa (Blue Moonrock x Blackberry Kush)
yield: 550g/m² indoors, up to 700g per plant outdoors
flavours: Blueberry, lavender, blackberry with light citrus note
medicinal: Pain, anxiety, ms and sleep disorders, deep sleep, calming

title: Sugar Cake
description: Sugar Cake by Black Farm Genetics is a cross of Divorce Cake x Jungle Cake. This 60% Indica 40% Sativa has a flowering time of 8-10 Weeks. This specific composition suggests that Sugar Cake leans more towards the relaxing and sedating effects associated with Indica strains.

The presence of Sativa genetics in Sugar Cake's lineage suggests that it may also offer some uplifting and energizing effects, which can help to balance out its relaxing qualities and provide a more well-rounded experience for users.
variety: 60% Indica 40% Sativa (Divorce Cake x Jungle Cake)
medicinal: Calmness, relaxation, sleep aid, uplifting and energizing effects

title: Bubblegum Sherbet
description: Bubble Gum Sherb was developed from an extremely potent female, Bubble Gum x Sunset Sherbet, that has a particularly pronounced terpene and cannabinoid profile. Both parent plants were selected through a long process of searching for flavor and potency to finally obtain the properties we had envisioned.

This strain is not recommended for the faint of heart or beginners as its extreme THC content of 30%-32% and the extensive cannabinoid profile ensure long-lasting and very intense effects. It gives us euphoric effects accompanied by body relaxation.
variety: Mainly Indica (Bubble Gum x Sunset Sherbet)
flavours: Berry, sweet, earthy, bubble gum aroma
medicinal: Stress, anxiety, sleep disorders, euphoric, happy, relaxed

title: Bruce Banger
description: Bruce Banger was created by crossing the original OG Kush with Strawberry Diesel. It is a sativa-dominant plant with the diesel/fuel character of the Strawberry parent yet with the power of Kush underlying the effect.

It takes up to 10 weeks to complete flowering, sometimes a little more, and makes for a great day-time high with energy and creativity. Bruce Banger can be grown indoors, outdoors or in a greenhouse and is adaptable with respect to grow media.
variety: Sativa Dominant (Strawberry Diesel X Walker Kush)
flavours: Earthy, floral, fruity
medicinal: Day-time high with energy and creativity

title: Pink Mango Gelato
description: Pink Mango Gelato is an Indica dominant hybrid, with its genetic parents being, White Widow x Somango & Pink Gelato. This medium-sized plant must not be underestimated, with THC levels of between 18 - 23% and a short flowering time of just 6 - 8 weeks.

The strain has an incredibly balanced body and mental effects. The creeping body high takes shape in the arms, legs, eyes and the temple area, while the White Widow comes in shortly after with cerebrally energetic euphoria that compliments the couch-lock.
variety: Indica dominant hybrid (White Widow x Somango & Pink Gelato)
flavours: Sweet mango with distinct skunky, earthy flavor
medicinal: Balanced body and mental effects, creeping body high, cerebrally energetic euphoria

title: Gas Face
description: Gas Face will hit you in the face with her dank, pungent fuel aroma. Bred in the US by a very famous breeder, and from equally famous parent strains, it's no wonder that Gas Face is getting a lot of attention from both recreational and medical users.

Gas Face is a very potent hybrid strain that produces around 25% THC and as high as 33%. Its dense, resinous flowers also contain a rich mix of terpenes, the most dominant being caryophyllene, limonene, and pinene.
variety: Hybrid
flavours: Dank, pungent fuel aroma
medicinal: Insomnia and sleep issues, stress, anxiety, depression, appetite loss, mood disorders, pain, inflammation, ptsd

title: Beach Wedding
description: Beach Wedding combines two of the most elite strains in modern cannabis. With permission from SEEDJUNKY GENETICS, we have combined the undeniable monster that is Wedding Cake with our own elite Tropicana Cookies.

This strain like most of our gear is created with extraction in mind and this girl will deliver in that department massively. Beach Wedding takes on a beautiful dark purple coloring and a delicious taste of cookie dough and orange.
variety: Hybrid (Wedding Cake x Tropicana Cookies)
yield: Famous for her production of flowers and of resin
flavours: Cookie dough and orange, warm spice

title: Infatuation
description: Infatuation is one of the captivating strains from the exclusive Blue Power 10 Year Anniversary Limited Edition Line. To create this top-notch hybrid, a Jealousy BX was crossed with Blue Power IX2.

Thanks to this connection, Infatuation boasts a 30% Sativa and 70% Indica genetic. Cultivators can anticipate bountiful yields ranging from 500 to 800 grams per square meter. Prepare to be smitten by the enchanting allure of Infatuation's unique character and remarkable flavors.
variety: 30% Sativa / 70% Indica (Jealousy BX x Blue Power IX2)
flavours: Sour, gas, sherbert, gelato

title: Lemon Cherry Belts breed
description: Lemon Cherry Belts is an mostly Indica from Lit Farms and can be cultivated indoors and outdoors. Where the plants will need a flowering time of approximately 65 days.
This strain combines the lineage of Rainbow Belts X Lemon Cherry Gelato, creating a unique mostly Indica variety suitable for various growing conditions.
variety: Mostly Indica (Rainbow Belts X Lemon Cherry Gelato)

title: Jet Fuel Gelato
description: Jet Fuel Gelato is the child of two legendary strains: Jet Fuel and Gelato. Its effects tend to be euphoric and uplifting, leaving consumers both happy and still functional enough to get tasks completed.

Immediately after smoking this powerhouse, users have described feeling a jolt of energy then leveling off into a dream-like euphoria. The flavor profile is also quite unique, combining the sweet, dessert-like taste of Gelato with the diesel aroma of Jet Fuel.
variety: Hybrid
flavours: Sweet, dessert-like taste of Gelato with diesel aroma of Jet Fuel
medicinal: euphoric and uplifting, energy, dream-like euphoria

title: Peanut Butter and Jelly
description: Explore the delightful Peanut Butter and Jelly Strain a balanced hybrid that combines the best of its parent strains Peanut Butter Breath and Jelly Breath. Known for its harmonious effects and distinct flavor profile, this strain offers a THC content ranging from 19% to 23% with minimal CBD.

Peanut Butter Breath contributes to the strain's relaxing and euphoric effects, while Jelly Breath brings fruity undertones and a balanced high. Together, these genetics create a hybrid strain that offers a blend of happiness, euphoria, and relaxation, making it suitable for daytime or evening use.
variety: Balanced hybrid
height: Indoor: 3-5 feet, Outdoor: up to 8 feet
yield: Indoor: up to 400 g/m², Outdoor: up to 550 g per plant
flavours: nutty and earthy aroma with fruity undertones

title: PINEAPPLE EXPRESS
description: Experience tropical bliss with this potent hybrid, born from the union of Big Bud and Skunk genetics. The Pineapple Express is an Indica-dominant variety that has been one of our best-selling strains for years!

With its short flowering time, bountiful harvests, and high THC levels it is a favourite among growers. Expect large, resinous, heavy, and compact flower heads with both aroma and taste strongly marked with lemon and pineapple notes.
variety: 70% Indica | 30% Sativa
flavours: Intense lemon, pineapple

title: Skunkberry
description: This hybrid's harmonious fusion of the Blueberry and Skunk strains makes it the pinnacle of cannabis craftsmanship. This hybrid, a masterpiece of the balancing genre, is the offspring of Skunk and Blueberry. Skunkberry ensures a strong and exciting voyage with a THC level that ranges from 20% to 40%.

An olfactory symphony that is both energizing and calming is produced by the combination of the terpenes Delta 3 Carene, Camphene, Phellandrene, Caryophyllene, and Pinene. You'll experience a sense of uplift and an unwavering joy that makes you laugh.
variety: Hybrid (Blueberry x Skunk)
yield: Indoor: 340 g/m², Outdoor: 350 g per plant
flavours: fruity sweetness, skunky flavor, blueberries, lemony aroma

title: Kosher Tangie Kush
description: Kosher Tangie Kush is the product of a breeding program featuring parent strains Kosher Kush and Tangie. Kosher Kush is an old-school variety that is well-respected, and Tangie is a relatively new kid on the block that hosts a delicious, citrusy terpene profile.

This combination results in a strain that tastes phenomenal and houses such high levels of THC that it is advised for experienced smokers only. The high induced is defined as a long-lasting body buzz.
variety: Indica-dominant (60%)
height: Indoor: up to 1.5m, Outdoor: up to 3m
flavours: Earthy, pungent citrus
